## Docker commands used to build the application 
docker build -t techtrends .

## Docker commands used to run the application
docker run -d -p 7111:7111 techtrends
# Access the application on: http://127.0.0.1:7111/ or http://localhost:7111/ or http://0.0.0.0:7111/

## Docker commands used to get the application logs
docker tag techtrends onurcariad/techtrends:v1.0.0

## Logs from the container running the TechTrends application
docker push onurcariad/techtrends:v1.0.0


